<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_174_r1l21">. <expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> . Apell Als vvir euch nehſt <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von Karl </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l22"><expan>holcʒſ<ex>chuhers</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>B<ex>urgers</ex></expan> vnd <expan>Ratgeſelle<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd Mıchels ſeins </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l23">dyeners wegen . 
<del rend="strikethrough">Als Jr vns dy <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan></del> der langcʒeit her </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l24">ſein dyener geweſen vnd noch ıſt / Als Jr vnd dıe ewrn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l25">den bey Swebiſchen vverd gefangen vnd Jm ein pferd das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l26">des <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>B<ex>urgers</ex></expan> ıſt mitſampt <expan>etlich<ex>er</ex></expan> anderr habe <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l27">vnd gen Burlaſwag gefürt habt / Darauff vns von euch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l28">noch kein <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> worden iſt / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> . daʒ Jr durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>vville<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l29"><expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>B<ex>urgers</ex></expan> dyener ledig laſſen vnd Jm das ſein <expan>vvid<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l30"><expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd volgen laſſen wöllet Als etc das wollen etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l31">vnd lat vns des noch ewr gütlich <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>wid<ex>er</ex>vviſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_174_r1l32">bey diſem <expan>pote<ex>n</ex></expan> . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>r</ex>ıa</expan> ṽ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Mıchaelis </ab>
